<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.8">
<l>malaiyataṉā laṇaikaṭṭi matiḷilaṅkai yaḻittavaṉē</l>
<l>yalaikaṭalaik kaṭaintamarark kamutaruḷic ceytavaṉē</l>
<l>kalaivalavar tāmvāḻuṅ kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>cilaivalavā cēvakaṉē cīrāmā tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Building a bridge with hills, O You who destroyed the fortressed Laṅkā!</l>
<l>Churning the wavy sea, O You who bestowed nectar upon the immortals!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram where exponents in arts live!</l>
<l>O capable Archer! O Warrior! O Śrīrāma, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
